list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Initial upload of the Pretix to Datacool converter application.
Features included: - Modular architecture (MVC pattern with config, logic, gui). - Modern GUI using CustomTkinter with animations and dark mode support. - Smart data cleaning: City names (regex), Name casing, and Country code translation via pycountry. - Excel Export: Automated formatting, column mapping, and empty cell highlighting. - Status Filtering: Option to filter by payment status (Paid/Open).
